{"tid":493334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"快閃九州溫泉遊","createTime":"2017-12-08T11:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T12:41:42.000Z","uid":134401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ccfc13e060be1a8b9410bcaefa2703f3025a9ae6","tid":493334,"uid":134401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:55:13.000Z","msg":"今次係我第一次去九州。坐港龍到福岡，到咗埗之後，已經係下午三點幾。我哋即刻去拎車。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/194711_098a05a1ea106bb1901596892971fed4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F194711_098a05a1ea106bb1901596892971fed4.jpg&h=e78f679b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/194713_cebd1a0cc478a2847626d32789f9b1c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F194713_cebd1a0cc478a2847626d32789f9b1c8.jpg&h=80183c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後我哋就揸車，去咗個叫大名嘅地方。因為天氣實在太凍頂唔順去Starbucks買左個暖笠笠既butter biscuit食。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/195122_b8dbb144da66515bdd6fd3c96a9bcd99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F195122_b8dbb144da66515bdd6fd3c96a9bcd99.jpg&h=df8dad54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/195124_f21bafcbc915030731761fc5f965d57f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F195124_f21bafcbc915030731761fc5f965d57f.jpg&h=f15edab5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/195125_05ac76fd12ac29b4e674ecea87a526f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F195125_05ac76fd12ac29b4e674ecea87a526f0.jpg&h=10cd5408&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/195127_60d6504fbc09c67dac6f1c700f6533ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F195127_60d6504fbc09c67dac6f1c700f6533ed.jpg&h=7d734de7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夜晚就去咗間叫華蓮既餐廳食。sukiyaki真係無得頂。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/195503_a92f7bfe3c5ec7ef37665957cce43485.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F195503_a92f7bfe3c5ec7ef37665957cce43485.jpg&h=e7938879&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/195505_4f164f5f9d19b4b8b753393c2125cc17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F195505_4f164f5f9d19b4b8b753393c2125cc17.jpg&h=aa9e6c08&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/195506_8a04b181248edafd8b9b924a8ed50932.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F195506_8a04b181248edafd8b9b924a8ed50932.jpg&h=ae1f4d22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72a2b459b5fe6c9f0526905f52c055dfdb70352a","tid":493334,"uid":134401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:57:12.000Z","msg":"哎呀開錯台添。。有冇得轉返去旅遊台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b899788135337cb428d8236b306ffd8b004c956","tid":493334,"uid":134401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T12:11:41.000Z","msg":"第一晚住福岡 candeo hotel，有溫泉浸。第二日朝早食左eggs n things，個pancake幾好食。之後就出發去睇呢個鍋之瀧瀑布。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/200840_7053b290b10ab5876be581d08d3fcbfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F200840_7053b290b10ab5876be581d08d3fcbfe.jpg&h=7e912cff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/200842_aace18b086afaae3983362b78ce22044.jpg\